<h1 class="text-center"> Project Credo: Grab Research by the Paper!</h1>

<div class='row'>
  <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-3 curate"><h2>Curate</h2></div>
  <div class="col-md-2 text-center document"><h2>Document</h2></div>
  <div class="col-md-2 text-center share"><h2>Share</h2></div>
</div>

<h4 class="text-center">We built a tool to make it easy for everyone to curate, document, and share research papers.  Our mission is to make it simple to understand research as a community.</h4>
<h4 class="text-center"><%= link_to 'Sign up and take control of research.', new_user_registration_path %> </h4>


<div class='divider'></div>

<div class='row text-center'>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
    <h2>Tutorial</h2>
    <p><%= link_to 'Checkout our tutorial', user_list_path(@tutorial.owner, @tutorial) %> to see how a to create and contribute to a list.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Sponsor Us</h2>
    <p><%= link_to 'Help us to keep the lights on through our patreon page', 'https://www.patreon.com/projectcredo', target: '_blank' %> where you can also join our mailing list!</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='row text-center'>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
    <h2>Issues</h2>
    <p>See an issue or want to contribute?  Tell us on our <%= link_to 'github page', 'https://github.com/briankung/projectcredo', target: '_blank' %>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>We'd love to hear from you. Contact us at help@projectcredo.com, </p>
  </div>
</div>